data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.AccountRemoval
data.value: Inactive accounts are deleted after 90 days for storage and privacy reasons.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.AgeRequirement
data.value: To use UmbraSync services you must be over 18 years old, or 21 in certain jurisdictions.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.Bandwidth
data.value: If you have a limited internet connection, additional charges may apply depending on how many files you send and receive. Files are compressed to save bandwidth, but varying speeds may delay syncing.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.Caution
data.value: The developer did their best to keep you safe, but there is no such thing as zero risk. Do not pair blindly with random people.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.Deletion
data.value: You can delete your account at any time. Your account and all associated data will be removed within 14 days.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.Inactivity
data.value: After a period of inactivity, mods stored on the UmbraSync server are automatically deleted.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.Infrastructure
data.value: UmbraSync infrastructure is hosted in the European Union (Germany) and Switzerland. Do not upload content that violates the laws of those countries.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.ModUpload
data.value: All mods currently active on your character and related states are automatically uploaded to the UmbraSync server you registered on. Only the files required for synchronization are transferred, not the full mod.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.Privacy
data.value: Uploaded files remain confidential and are only distributed to paired users who request the exact same files. Be careful who you pair with.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Agreement.TimeoutLabel
data.value: 'I agree' button will be available in {0}s

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Storage.Description
data.value: To not unnecessary download files already present on your computer, Umbra will have to scan your Penumbra mod directory. Additionally, a local storage folder must be set where Umbra will download other character files to. Once the storage folder is set and the scan complete, this page will automatically forward to registration at a service.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Storage.InvalidPenumbraPath
data.value: You do not have a valid Penumbra path set. Open Penumbra and set up a valid path for the mod directory.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Storage.Note
data.value: Note: The initial scan, depending on the amount of mods you have, might take a while. Please wait until it is completed.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Storage.UseCompactorDescription
data.value: The File Compactor can save a tremendeous amount of space on the hard disk for downloads through Umbra. It will incur a minor CPU penalty on download but can speed up loading of other characters. It is recommended to keep it enabled. You can change this setting later anytime in the Umbra settings.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Storage.WarningFileCache
data.value: Warning: once past this step you should not delete the FileCache.csv of Umbra in the Plugin Configurations folder of Dalamud. Otherwise on the next launch a full re-scan of the file cache database will be initiated.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Storage.WarningScan
data.value: Warning: if the scan is hanging and does nothing for a long time, chances are high your Penumbra folder is not set up properly.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Welcome.Description
data.value: Umbra is a plugin that will replicate your full current character state including all Penumbra mods to other paired users. Note that you will have to have Penumbra as well as Glamourer installed to use this plugin.

data.name: CompactUi.IntroUi.Welcome.ModNote
data.value: Note: Any modifications you have applied through anything but Penumbra cannot be shared and your character state on other clients might look broken because of this or others players mods might not apply on your end altogether. If you want to use this plugin you will have to move your mods to Penumbra.
